list.name: Default
list.comment: - Changed AppVersion to 0.0.3 and VersionCode to 3 - Added workspace.xml to git to commit run configuration - Added run-configuragtions: - Build Release APK: Build release APK-File - Android Release: Runs release APK-File on debug device -

task.summary: - Adding project to GitHub - Added Php-Scripts for converting html-file to json string - In-App features: - My Class Tab: Select own class and see all available substitutes for that class - All Classes Tab: Displays a list of all classes that currently have substitutes in planing - Calendar View: Displays all substitutes by Date - Settings View: Shows the App Icon, Version and co. - Contact button for writing an email and copying dev email to clipboard - Open substitute plan in browser button - delete local cache button
- Adding comments and documentation to the utils.js
- Added several comments, TODOs - Reformatted some files with the autoformation - Cleaned up some code
- Small changes to prevent IDEA warnings
- Added IDEA project files - removed unused packages
- Added weekday to the header in all substitute-tables
- Added abstract component for all refreshable Views, called RefreshScrollView
- Implemented abstract RefreshScrollView in Substitute-, Calendar- and Class-View
- Implemented abstract RefreshScrollView in Substitute-, Calendar- and Class-View - Changed version to 0.0.2 and versioncode to 2
